&lt;h1&gt;Deputy Directorate Manager&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen within the Surgery, Women&#39;s and Children&#39;s Division for a Deputy Directorate Manager to support general and specialty surgery services. This role is integral to support the operational management of surgical services, ensure key national standards are met and support the organisations restoration of elective services.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a permanent Band 7 management role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For any informal queries please contact Michelle Treanor, Directorate Manager - Surgery, Trauma and Orthopaedics on 0161 922 5125 or michelle.treanor@tgh.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;INTERVIEW DATE: 17th November 2020&lt;/p&gt;
